_sText:
After far too long, my first real attempt at a map is finally here. Wanted to make something that resembled the older maps of surf, in both form and function, along with a few other interesting gimmicks. Big thanks to the testers and everyone else who helped with the map. Also a big thanks to the Momentum Mod mapping discord for answering my dumb questions. Let me know what you think and enjoy the map!

Thanks to draph for the showcase video!

T4 Linear, 3500 maxvel
